{"tid":1636481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 Be Wolf  因為狼，已經被獵豹逼上絕路","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:07:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T18:56:14.000Z","uid":35584,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6614d2675278417f0a64f8b30878089bf9dac4","tid":1636481,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:07:23.000Z","msg":"『從小，父親就教我一個道理。<br />\n <br />\n「爸爸！！點解電視上面俾獵豹追捕嘅個隻狼突然間停低回頭，好兇狠咁望住獵豹嘅？」<br />\n <br />\n他跟我說：「因為狼，已經被獵豹迫上絕路。」<br />\n<br />\n草源上萬惡的獵豹並不可怕，最可怕的是&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n <br />\n被迫上絕路的狼。<br />\n<br />\n「思雨，你知道狼嘅特性？」老爸問。<br />\n <br />\n「唔知&hellip;」年幼的我又怎會知。<br />\n <br />\n「就係佢哋唔會放棄同伴。」老爸站了起來，逐一望向我們單車鋪裡的員工：「就算手要斷、腳要甩&hellip;&hellip;都唔可以放棄佢哋。」<br />\n <br />\n『狼​雖​然​通​常​獨​自​活​動​，​但​狼​卻​是​最​團​結​的​動​物​，​你​不​會​發​現​有​哪​隻​狼​在​同​伴​受​傷​時​獨​自​逃​走​&hellip;&hellip;因此，你不要做隻膽小逃跑的羊，也不要做因為饑餓而吃掉自己同伴的獵豹&hellip;&hellip;你是隻狼。』<br />\n<br />\n十少年2 &ndash;&ndash;&ndash; 墨說<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n沙田新城市一戰 手足被逼上絕路<br />\n掀起勇武第一次打狗反抗<br />\n<br />\n如今我地再冇退路<br />\n<br />\n香港人 Be Wolf  <br />\n<br />\n唔好再放棄同伴<br />\n<br />\n打狗 救人</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"a5a3e3183553265be5b045cd4f928b9ee0d36038","tid":1636481,"uid":35584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:09:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">打狗 救人</span>"},{"pid":"0bb70cda469f450661998cbba1f81ad722ddd155","tid":1636481,"uid":61831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVf%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=85321e10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a> TWITTER戰線要人!!!, 每人出少少力已經幫到好多<br />\n<br />\n讓狼的嚎叫傳出國際吧"},{"pid":"d7c673abea12008e1fb932563621ee3bffea1bfe","tid":1636481,"uid":35584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s